cs.SI, cs.SD, cs.SOC, cs.CYBER, cs.HC 

Reasoning: 
- cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) is the most likely category as the paper analyzes a large-scale mobile phone call dataset to gain insight into social closeness in pairs of individuals. 
- cs.SD (Software Engineering) is also a possible category as the paper may involve software tools and techniques for analyzing the dataset. 
- cs.SOC (Social and Behavioral Sciences) is another possible category as the paper deals with social relationships and communication patterns. 
- cs.CYBER (Cybersecurity and Privacy) is a possible category as the paper may involve privacy concerns related to the use of mobile phone call data. 
- cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction) is also a possible category as the paper may involve designing interfaces or systems for analyzing and visualizing the data.
